title: Newly leaked images show us more of the Motorola Moto E32
content:
Motorola hasn’t really taken command of the Android smartphone segment in quite some time. While it has had some interesting offerings over the past few years, mainly in the foldable smartphone category with its Razr 5G, most of its devices have been overshadowed by releases from Samsung, OnePlus, and others.
